What is a PPM Tool?
A PPM (Project Portfolio Management) tool is a software solution designed to help businesses plan, manage, and optimize multiple projects efficiently. It enables strategic project selection, resource allocation, risk management, and performance tracking across an organizationâ€™s entire project portfolio. Unlike basic project management tools, which focus on individual project execution, a PPM tool provides a holistic view of all projects, ensuring they align with business objectives.

